public class CheckBoxButton
extends CheckBox
implements HasActive, HasType<ButtonType>, HasSize<ButtonSize>, HasIcon, HasIconPosition

Button representing a checkbox used within a ButtonGroup that has toggle set to Toogle.BUTTONS.

If you are looking for a classic checkbox see CheckBox.

Author:
Sven Jacobs
